        "id": 1007275
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-19T18:22:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s not easy (in Go or CUE) to validate a slice with alternative `string` and `any` members, and the code is straightforward to deal with the two parallel slices. There are a few realistic Go implementations of these functions in the PoC, and I\u0027ve added a link to that CL now.",
      "parentUuid": "e1ef692c_974c2f65",
      "revId": "9c92333dfad055d156b42db1e14200135df4eb86",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
